他european language，學完既話學其他language易好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea589f9228a9c2e33a601f2d89c06b04279bcec4","tid":164689,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自學緊latin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上唔會用黎同人溝通，但係對academic有幫助（好多terms都用番latin，因為佢地係dead language所以個definition唔會隨時間改變）<br />\n同埋Latin既grammar複雜過其他european language，學完既話學其他language易好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oJ8n_Y6bJ_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoJ8n_Y6bJ_s&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=b564c9fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oJ8n_Y6bJ_s</a><br />\n暫時拉丁文畀我既印象係用黎show off <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可唔可以將latin同其他european languages比較下? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418917bf50eb76a00f7ac4822e51beb3ac04aba6","tid":164689,"uid":93142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自學緊latin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上唔會用黎同人溝通，但係對academic有幫助（好多terms都用番latin，因為佢地係dead language所以個definition唔會隨時間改變）<br />\n同埋Latin既grammar複雜過其他european language，學完既話學其他language易好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oJ8n_Y6bJ_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoJ8n_Y6bJ_s&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=b564c9fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oJ8n_Y6bJ_s</a><br />\n暫時拉丁文畀我既印象係用黎show off <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可唔可以將latin同其他european languages比較下? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Romance_languages#Samples\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FRomance_languages%23Samples&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=6e577c0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Romance_languages#Samples</a><br />\n<br />\nLatin 係歐洲國家用開既語言，一直系elite class／church用左十幾世紀，之後唔知點樣derive左vulgar latin，再慢慢成為各種現代語言（Spanish french Italian ）同influence各種語言（例如英文有好似70%既字都有latin既元素）<br />\n<br />\nlatin比人感覺似show off我諗係因為以前（我指中世紀果時）得elite 貴族同教會先會講（平民唔識字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n但係認真學既話佢都有好多平民用語 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過如果本身想學西班牙文／法文既話其實係唔需要學latin先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非linguistic expert"},{"pid":"0140b90dacef963afd48bc841c9f9837c477a56c","tid":164689,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:01:32.000Z","msg":"歐洲教堂大時大節唱聖詩會用latin，學左可以原汁原味咁聽d歌詞"},{"pid":"bd4c6a9762bf8e8d86c731522bb25ac85f554cf4","tid":164689,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自學緊latin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上唔會用黎同人溝通，但係對academic有幫助（好多terms都用番latin，因為佢地係dead language所以個definition唔會隨時間改變）<br />\n同埋Latin既grammar複雜過其他european language，學完既話學其他language易好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oJ8n_Y6bJ_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoJ8n_Y6bJ_s&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=b564c9fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oJ8n_Y6bJ_